   Avast!  Try this one swabbies.  Here's a table of English to Pirate translations

   .. table::

      ==========  ==============
      English     Pirate
      ==========  ==============
      sir         Senor
      hotel       hotel
      student     estudiante
      boy         nino
      madam       senora
      professor   profesor
      restaurant  restaurante
      your        su
      excuse      disculpe
      students    estudiantes
      are         son
      lawyer      abogado
      the         El
      restroom    bano
      my          mi
      hello       hola
      is          es
      man         hombre
      ==========  ==============

   Write a program that asks the user for a sentence in English and then translates that sentence to Spanish.
   ~~~~